column5: Saw a sweet boat for sale Jumped on the deal  Spent two days on the general clean up and today adding a 7" LCX lowrance on the dash to go with the 102c on the bow  anyhow the new triton tr18 looking forward to whippin some bass
Nice....but personally, I liked the starcraft better  I'm not a bass fisherman though!  Sinker
You can't be much of a fisherman. That's the kind of boat that would call out to me. Looks great. Who needs fishing? Just burn some gas.  JF
sweet ride...all the best to you and your boat.....
Congrats    you got yourself one great boat
I've been looking at getting one of those for a couple of years now, what year is that one?
sweet boat!! whats on the back?
thanks 150 vmax on the back of it.
You'll be skipping o'er the crests!
If I were to buy another,that would be it. Nice ride.
nice....looking forward to yet another maiden voyage report !!!
